{"tid":771734,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"真心請教 的士唔係頭2km 24咩？","createTime":"2018-08-08T08:06:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-26T19:50:08.000Z","uid":163191,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"2f9b4808f366d8d2f4e131c249c9b2cfcc6722a7","tid":771734,"uid":163191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T08:06:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/08/160459_0af9f32973d01dc80477f837757e9cd8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F08%2F160459_0af9f32973d01dc80477f837757e9cd8.png&h=b73cfbae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我諗大家都有搭過呢類標既的士，<br />\n<br />\n佢有個distance架嘛，<br />\n<br />\n我諗起由細到大，到岩岩呢次，<br />\n<br />\n佢去到1.7km就跳左<br />\n<br />\n其實係咪真係2km唔會跳？"},{"pid":"11b4b24d369b3e91da10899540f8051d2629d861","tid":771734,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T08:07:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db36711adbf76fa80921f60fbbc68e98f3fff6b9","tid":771734,"uid":33694,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T08:08:30.000Z","msg":"停車時間都好似要計"},{"pid":"c12b90c8ffed00dc5a0041ab9c1b9e1eb30ace63","tid":771734,"uid":102132,"like":1,"dislike":27,"score":-26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T08:08:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0b3ba1dbbf437abf42db4b6ffa6681e0eff1532e","tid":771734,"uid":84212,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T08:45:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a5414832d28cd050ea1b86912efc7cc49d551044","tid":771734,"uid":88817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T08:46:11.000Z","msg":"推，我都想問"},{"pid":"ad7f37c74b5b30f000d2d8dcac03ae9e1c5b53f9","tid":771734,"uid":188418,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T08:47:35.000Z","msg":"我覺得呢類都做過手腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖然唔識"},{"pid":"ab1d1